ol.li:
In your customization css match the topic from the
                CSS and associate it a named page. This page has landscape orientation and small
                margins.*[class ~= "topic/topic"][outputclass = 'wide'] {
    page: wide-page;
}

@page wide-page {
    size: letter landscape;
    margin: 0.5in;
}

body.note:
You can extend the example on any DITA element that should be displayed on wider page. Change the CSS
            selector
            to:*[outputclass = 'wide'] {
    page: wide-page;
}
